::Scrap::

Scrap hops into the jet after Banzai-Tron.

"Allright, Supernova, its all you," he says, relaxing in his seat. 
The jet lifts off the air and then blasts off toward the Iron Fist. 
With two bots inside it, there was still room for one more, so Scrap 
and Banzai-Tron should be fairly comfortable.

"So what did happen to you?" Scrap asks Banzai-Tron, playing around 
with the weapon control systems inside the cockpit and destroying 
various trees as the jet passed over them.
